  "prompt": "How can I stop feeling restless?",
  "response": "Here are some strategies to help reduce restlessness:\n\n1. Physical techniques\n- Exercise regularly\n- Practice yoga or stretching\n- Take deep, slow breaths\n- Go for a walk\n- Try progressive muscle relaxation\n\n2. Mental techniques\n- Meditate\n- Practice mindfulness\n- Journal your thoughts\n- Listen to calming music\n- Limit caffeine and screen time\n\n3. Lifestyle adjustments\n- Maintain a consistent sleep schedule\n- Create a relaxing bedtime routine\n- Reduce stress\n- Practice time management\n- Get enough sleep\n\n4. Additional strategies\n- Talk to a therapist\n- Try anxiety-reducing techniques\n- Identify and address underlying causes\n- Consider herbal supplements like chamomile\n- Use grounding techniques\n\n5. If restlessness persists\n- Consult a healthcare professional\n- Check for potential underlying conditions\n- Discuss potential medication options\n\nChoose techniques that work best for you and be patient with yourself as you develop new coping strategies.\n\nWould you like me to elaborate on any of these suggestions?",
